\begin{equation}
\Delta = (\cos\alpha)(\beta\cos\alpha) - (\beta\sin\alpha)(-\sin\alpha) = \beta(\cos^2\alpha + \sin^2\alpha) = \beta
\end{equation}

Simplifying:

\begin{equation}
