where $A_{\times, A}$ is the gauge connection component in the direction $A$. When restricted to the electromagnetic $U(1)$ subgroup (generated by $T_{EM} = \frac{1}{3}(T_{t_x t_y} + T_{t_y t_z} + T_{t_z t_x})$ as correctly identified in our earlier analysis) and projected onto 4D spacetime, this becomes:

