where $\gamma^\mu$ are the 4D Dirac gamma matrices, $\omega_\mu^{\nu\rho}$ is the 4D spin connection, and $\gamma_{\nu\rho} = \frac{1}{2}[\gamma_\nu, \gamma_\rho]$ are the generators of the Lorentz group in the spinor representation.

