S_{7D} = \int_{\mathcal{M}^7} \bar{\Psi} \Gamma^A D_A \Psi \sqrt{g^{(7)}} d^7X + \int_{\mathcal{M}^7} \text{Tr}(F_{\times} \wedge \star F_{\times})
