S_{4D} = \int_{\mathcal{M}^4} \bar{\psi} (i \hbar \gamma^\mu D_\mu - mc) \psi \sqrt{-g^{(4)}} d^4x - \frac{1}{4} \int_{\mathcal{M}^4} F_{\mu\nu} F^{\mu\nu} \sqrt{-g^{(4)}} d^4x
