\subsection{The QCD Lagrangian from 7D Action}

\subsubsection{Complete 7D Action with $SU(3)$ Gauge Fields}

The action for QCD in our 7D framework is a natural extension of the action we derived for QED, incorporating the $SU(3)$ gauge structure:

\begin{equation}
S_{7D}^{QCD} = \int_{\mathcal{M}^7} \bar{\Psi}_q (\Gamma^A D_A - m_q) \Psi_q \sqrt{g^{(7)}} d^7X + \int_{\mathcal{M}^7} \text{Tr}(F_{\times}^{SU(3)} \wedge \star F_{\times}^{SU(3)})
